        <title type="html"><![CDATA[v1 更新日志]]></title>
        <id>https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v1/</id>
        <link href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v1/"/>
        <updated>2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[{/* ### 新增]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="105">1.0.5<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v1/#105" class="hash-link" aria-label="1.0.5的直接链接" title="1.0.5的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<h4 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="修复-">修复 🐛<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v1/#%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D-" class="hash-link" aria-label="修复 🐛的直接链接" title="修复 🐛的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h4>
<ul>
<li class="">修复 ModalForm 组件当 initialValues 变更后，打开弹窗时应该显示新的值。</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="104">1.0.4<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v1/#104" class="hash-link" aria-label="1.0.4的直接链接" title="1.0.4的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<h4 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="修复--1">修复 🐛<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v1/#%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D--1" class="hash-link" aria-label="修复 🐛的直接链接" title="修复 🐛的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h4>
<ul>
<li class="">ProTable 组件修复 <code>enableDelete</code> 为函数时返回对象中 <code>visible: false</code> 不生效的问题。当 <code>enableDelete</code> 函数返回 <code>{ visible: false }</code> 时，删除按钮现在会正确隐藏。</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="103">1.0.3<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v1/#103" class="hash-link" aria-label="1.0.3的直接链接" title="1.0.3的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<h4 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="修复--2">修复 🐛<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v1/#%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D--2" class="hash-link" aria-label="修复 🐛的直接链接" title="修复 🐛的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h4>
<ul>
<li class="">Button 组件添加 <code>forwardRef</code> 支持,修复在 Ant Design v6 的 Popconfirm 组件中的定位问题。</li>
<li class="">LinkButton 组件添加 <code>forwardRef</code> 支持。</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="100">1.0.0<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v1/#100" class="hash-link" aria-label="1.0.0的直接链接" title="1.0.0的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>1.0 版本全面覆盖了测试用例。代码覆盖率大于 90%，分支覆盖率大于 85%。</p>
<!-- -->
<p>从 v0 版本迁移请关注下面的变更项。</p>
<h4 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="新增-">新增 🆕<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v1/#%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E-" class="hash-link" aria-label="新增 🆕的直接链接" title="新增 🆕的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h4>
<ul>
<li class="">组件库增加多语言支持。</li>
<li class="">组件库支持 SSR。</li>
<li class="">增加 utils 工具方法 <a class="" href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/components/utils-tree/">utils-tree</a>。</li>
<li class="">SchemaForm 组件增加 <a class="" href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/components/schema-form/#%E5%8F%AA%E8%AF%BB%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F">只读表格模式</a>。</li>
<li class="">ProTable 组件增加 <code>delSuccessProps</code> 属性。</li>
</ul>
<h4 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="变更-">变更 💥<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v1/#%E5%8F%98%E6%9B%B4-" class="hash-link" aria-label="变更 💥的直接链接" title="变更 💥的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h4>
<ul>
<li class="">ProTable 组件属性变更（<code>modalProps</code> 和 <code>formProps</code> 合并成 <code>modalFormProps</code>）。</li>
<li class="">ProTable 组件属性名变更（<code>confirmModelType</code> 改成 <code>delConfirmType</code>）。</li>
<li class="">ProTable 组件属性变更（<code>confirmModalProps</code> 移除，改成 <code>delPopconfirmProps</code> 和 <code>delModalConfirmProps</code>）。</li>
<li class="">ProTable 组件属性名变更（<code>optionColSpaceSize</code> 改成 <code>optionColumnSpaceProps</code>）。</li>
<li class="">ProTable 组件导出功能变更：<!-- -->
<ol>
<li class="">移除了 exceljs 库的默认依赖，这有助于减少组件库的体积。</li>
<li class="">对于需要导出的页面，需要先安装 exceljs 库，然后调用相关的方法。<a class="" href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/components/protable/#%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE">参考文档</a></li>
</ol>
</li>
<li class="">FormUpload 组件移除了给 children 默认注入 loading 属性的功能。改成给 children 函数提供 loading 属性。</li>
</ul>
<h4 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="类型-">类型 <img width="20" src="data:image/png;base64," style="vertical-align:-3px"><a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v1/#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B-" class="hash-link" aria-label="类型-的直接链接" title="类型-的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h4>
<ul>
<li class="">ProForm 组件 <code>submitter</code> 属性支持 boolean 类型。</li>
</ul>]]></content>
    </entry>
    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[v0 更新日志]]></title>
        <id>https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/</id>
        <link href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/"/>
        <updated>2025-01-02T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[{/ truncate /}]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0511">0.5.11<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0511" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.5.11的直接链接" title="0.5.11的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>ModalForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">style: 修复长表单时的滚动条.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0510">0.5.10<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0510" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.5.10的直接链接" title="0.5.10的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>ModalForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛 消除 initialValue 相关告警.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="059">0.5.9<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#059" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.5.9的直接链接" title="0.5.9的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛 增加 pro-component 警告信息的捕获 <code>antd: Form.Item</code> .</li>
</ul>
<p>ModalForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛 initialValues 与 openModal 中初始值的合并处理.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="058">0.5.8<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#058" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.5.8的直接链接" title="0.5.8的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛 增加对 pro-component 警告信息的捕获, 例如 <code>Warning: findDOMNode is deprecated</code></li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="057">0.5.7<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#057" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.5.7的直接链接" title="0.5.7的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>BusinessSelect 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛修复 BusinessSelect 分组选项的问题.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="056">0.5.6<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#056" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.5.6的直接链接" title="0.5.6的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>BusinessSelect 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛修复 BusinessSelect 组件 disabled 属性未接收问题. 同时增加分组选项.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="055">0.5.5<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#055" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.5.5的直接链接" title="0.5.5的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>ModalForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">💄ModalForm 弹窗表单有滚动时滚动条贴边.</li>
</ul>
<p>SchemaForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛修复 schema 中 required 属性在 formItemProps 为函数时失效的问题.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="054">0.5.4<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#054" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.5.4的直接链接" title="0.5.4的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>BusinessSelect 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🆕增加 searchDebounceValue 属性, 控制组件搜索时的 debounce 值.</li>
<li class="">🐛修复组件搜索时 loading 和 allowClear 冲突的问题.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="053">0.5.3<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#053" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.5.3的直接链接" title="0.5.3的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>ProTable 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛修复搜索表单 valueType: dependency 无效的问题.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="051">0.5.1<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#051" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.5.1的直接链接" title="0.5.1的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2024-5-20</p>
<p>ProForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛修复 formRef 约定式赋值没有及时更新的问题.</li>
<li class="">🐛修复在 <code>embed</code> 模式下对 valueType: formList 的 grid 布局失效的问题.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="050">0.5.0<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#050" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.5.0的直接链接" title="0.5.0的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2024-5-15</p>
<ul>
<li class="">✨ 重构 SchemaForm, ProForm 的约定式实现. 修复了 fieldProps 函数中 form 约定式赋值无效的问题. 覆盖了测试用例.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="044">0.4.4<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#044" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.4.4的直接链接" title="0.4.4的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2024-5-11</p>
<p>SchemaForm 组件, ProForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛修复 <strong>表单实例</strong> 的 <code>validateFields</code>, <code>getFieldsFormatValue</code>, <code>validateFieldsReturnFormatValue</code> 方法未对约定式处理的问题.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="043">0.4.3<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#043" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.4.3的直接链接" title="0.4.3的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2024-5-6</p>
<p>ModalForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛修复 ModalForm 组件(或者 ProTable) 套嵌在 ProForm 组件中时, fieldProps 函数中的 form 被覆盖的问题.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="041">0.4.1<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#041" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.4.1的直接链接" title="0.4.1的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2024-4-25</p>
<p>SchemaForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛修复 getFieldsValue 没有对约定式值进行处理的问题.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="040">0.4.0<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#040" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.4.0的直接链接" title="0.4.0的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2024-4-12</p>
<p>移除掉在 antd v4中过期的 api. 所以在 v0.4 以后只支持 antd v5.</p>
<p>ModalForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">移除掉 bodyStyle api.</li>
</ul>
<p>SchemaForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🆕在只读模式下 render 函数的第二个参数由 entity 扩展成 record. 这个 record 不仅包含所有表单项的值, 还包含了 initialValues 里除表单项以外的值和 setFieldsValue 里除表单项以外的值, 增加了实用性.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0323">0.3.23<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0323" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.3.23的直接链接" title="0.3.23的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>同 0.4.4</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0322">0.3.22<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0322" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.3.22的直接链接" title="0.3.22的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>同 0.4.3</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0319">0.3.19<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0319" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.3.19的直接链接" title="0.3.19的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>同 0.4.1</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0318">0.3.18<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0318" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.3.18的直接链接" title="0.3.18的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2024-4-9</p>
<p>ProTable 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class=""><img width="20" src="data:image/png;base64," style="vertical-align:-3px"> 修复 ProTable 中 search 属性的类型定义.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0317">0.3.17<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0317" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.3.17的直接链接" title="0.3.17的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2024-4-9</p>
<p>文档用例更新成 antd v5.</p>
<p>ModalForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class=""><img width="20" src="data:image/png;base64," style="vertical-align:-3px"> 修复 ModalFormInnerRefType 的类型定义, 修复后 useRef() 默认值可以为空.</li>
</ul>
<p>ProTable 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class=""><img width="20" src="data:image/png;base64," style="vertical-align:-3px"> 修复 TableColumnType 的类型定义, 修复后提示更加准确.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0316">0.3.16<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0316" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.3.16的直接链接" title="0.3.16的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2024-2-11</p>
<p>ModalForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛修复 openModal('read') 只读方法对 dependency 里的子项无效的问题.</li>
</ul>
<p>ProTable 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛修复 innerRef 与 fieldProps 中的 innerRef 不是同对象的问题.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0315">0.3.15<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0315" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.3.15的直接链接" title="0.3.15的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2024-2-7</p>
<p>ProTable 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🛠schema 中的 type 字段新增 'search' 类型, 代表该项只会被用于 ProTable 的 search 区域.</li>
<li class="">🆕新增 defaultHideInSearch 属性, 来全局控制 column 是否默认显示在搜索区域.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0314">0.3.14<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0314" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.3.14的直接链接" title="0.3.14的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2024-2-2</p>
<p>ProTable 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🆕新增 reload 全局事件, 用于在其它页面控制表格的刷新.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0313">0.3.13<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0313" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.3.13的直接链接" title="0.3.13的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2023-12-3</p>
<p>ProTable 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛删除按钮增加 stopPropogation.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0312">0.3.12<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0312" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.3.12的直接链接" title="0.3.12的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2023-12-1</p>
<p>SchemaForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛修复约定式赋值问题: setFieldsValue 赋值时会把其它表单项的值赋空.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0311">0.3.11<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0311" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.3.11的直接链接" title="0.3.11的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2023-11-29</p>
<p>SchemaForm 组件</p>
<ul>
<li class="">🐛修复约定式赋值问题: 假设组件是 labelInValue 的, dataIndex 是 userId,userName, 当后端返回 userId 和 userName 为空时, 原先会给组件赋上空对象, 现在改成给组件赋 undefined.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_dkMQ" id="0310">0.3.10<a href="https://jaykou25.github.io/react-admin-kit/changelog/v0/#0310" class="hash-link" aria-label="0.3.10的直接链接" title="0.3.10的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>2023-11-28</p>
<p>BusinessSelect 组件</p>
<ul>
